(What This Topic Means) Tj
T*
(Tenses show the time of actions and help students write accurately. In English, students) Tj
T*
(do better when they understand not only the definition of Tenses, but also the language,) Tj
T*
(symbols, and patterns that appear whenever this topic is tested.) Tj
